constructor.description: Initializes the contract with the implementation logic address, admin address, and any initialization data.

fallback.description: Fallback function to receive Ether and handle unexpected function calls.

receive.description: Receive function to handle incoming Ether transfers.

AdminChanged.description: Emitted when the admin address is changed.

BeaconUpgraded.description: Emitted when the beacon address is upgraded.

Upgraded.description: Emitted when the implementation address is upgraded.
